    <p>LOS AN­GE­LES • The Indy</p>
    <p>500 slashed spectator ca­pac­ity for the sec­ond time in a month on Tues­day, but at 87,000 fans, it would still be­come the largest US sport­ing event since the coro­n­avirus pan­demic be­gan.</p>
    <p>Or­gan­is­ers said that at­ten­dance at the leg­endary mo­tor sport race on Aug 23 will now be lim­ited to 25 per cent in­stead of the 50 per cent ca­pac­ity an­nounced in June.</p>


